title: $500 RENT CREDIT! CALL TODAY!- 1 BR- Wexford Commons
posting_body: ['***RENT SPECIAL: $400 RENT CREDIT + ADDTIONAL $100 IF YOU APPLY THE SAME DAY AS YOUR SHOWING!', '*** CALL TODAY FOR MORE DETAILS', 'Looking for affordable living?', 'LOOK NO FURTHER!!', 'Wexford Commons Apartments offers 1 bedroom apartment homes for rent in South Minneapolis, bordering Richfield and close to the Hub Shopping Center.', 'It is close to many restaurants, shops, recreational opportunities, the bus line and much more.', 'Easy freeway access to downtown Minneapolis, Edina, Bloomington, and Mall of America.', 'Market Rent Starting at $950/month-', 'Available July-September!', 'Call today and let our professional staff give you a personal tour of the community.', '1 BR - Deposit starting at $400', 'Lease Terms: Month-to-Month Rental Agreements with a 9 Month Clause', '$40 Application Fee per Adult', 'Cats Accepted with the Following Restrictions:', 'Cats - $250 non-refundable pet fee, $30 monthly pet rent, a limit of 2 cats per apartment, and must be spayed/neutered.', 'Amenities:', '*Amazing Professional Staff That Understands That Service Counts', '*Expert Maintenance Team with 24-hour Emergency Assistance Available', '*Heat, Trash, Gas, Water and Sewer Paid', '*Air Conditioning in All Apartments', '*Window Coverings', '*Ceiling Fans', '*Some Balconies', '*Ample Closet Space', '*Accent Wall Colors', '*Dishwashers', '*Control Access Entries', '*Several Different Floor Plans to Choose From', '*Package Receiving', 'Year Built: 1960', '# of Buildings: 10', 'School District: Minneapolis', 'Bus Lines: 18', 'Number of Floors: 3', 'Parking: Off-Street Parking & Garages', 'Garages: $60/month', 'Laundry:', 'On-site, First Floor- Card Operated', 'Cable TV: Cable --Internet Ready', '*Prices and availability are subject to change at any time.']
